## Summary
This document explains Monthly Tracking Users (MTU) billing in Amplitude, detailing how MTUs are calculated (unique users triggering events within a calendar month), available plan limits (up to 1M MTUs), and how to monitor usage. It addresses common scenarios affecting MTU counts, including anonymous vs. identified users, cross-project tracking, and data backfills.

